Sentencas: The subsolidus phase equilibria in air for the Al2O3-CeO2-PbO and Al2O3-CeO2-RuO2 systems were studied with the aim of obtaining information on possible interactions between a CeO2-based solid electrolyte in solid-oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) and other oxides.
Titulo: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the Al2O3-CeO2-PbO and Al2O3-CeO2-RuO2 systems

Sentencas: No ternary compound was found in either of the systems.
Titulo: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the Al2O3-CeO2-PbO and Al2O3-CeO2-RuO2 systems

Sentencas: The tie line in the Al2O3-PbO-CeO2 system is between Al2Pb2O5 and the CeO2.
Titulo: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the Al2O3-CeO2-PbO and Al2O3-CeO2-RuO2 systems
